<HEADLINE>
<P>
JACK NICHOLSON 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Ah, how comforting to know that Hollywood celebrities are human like the rest 
of us. Witness the pimple in the crease of Jack Nicholson's nose. 
</P>
<P>
Why, I suspect that even these pampered, highly overpaid prima donnas put their 
pants on, one leg at a time, like Joe and Joanie Ordinary. 
</P>
<P>
IRMA E. BAKER 
</P>
<P>
La Canada Flintridge 
</P>
