<HEADLINE>
<P>
NOT A CROSS WORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Over the past five years, I've looked forward to the Puzzler. 
</P>
<P>
My husband and I have fought over who gets to start first. We've fed our 
children late dinners; paid Pacific Bell a fortune in exchanging clues, and 
used our dictionaries, encyclopedias and atlases to the point of knowing now 
why we forked over all that dough. I won't go into all the other details of 
what we go through to complete your puzzles each week. We just wanted you to 
know how much enjoyment the Puzzler gives us. 
</P>
<P>
DENNIS AND PAULA SIMILA 
</P>
<P>
Arroyo Grande 
</P>
</TEXT>
