(A1) COLOR, Marinovich in a Husky's grasp. ; Photo, USC's Ricky Ervins can't 
escape grip of Brett Collins (46) as Dave Hoffman (54) moves in. Ervins had 
five yards in nine carries. LORI SHEPLER / Los Angeles Times 
