FLAUNTING IT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Hurrah! The trend to build "monster" homes totally out of scale with their lot 
and neighborhood character may be halted by revising current building codes 
("Blockbuster Homes Could Get Busted By Revised Codes," Sept. 9.) 
</P>
<P>
La Jolla and Point Loma are not the only communities suffering from extravagant 
structures. 
</P>
<P>
