<TEXT>
<P>
Frances A. Hogestyn has been named president and chief executive of Griffin 
Enterprises, Newport Beach, succeeding Evan T. Hogestyn, who will be chairman 
of foreign investments. Her duties will include corporate and strategic 
planning, development of land projects, coordination of foreign investments and 
expansion of realty services. 
</P>
