<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
<P>
Football player -- Sunday's South Bay sports section erroneously reported that 
Carson High receiver Fred Sims fumbled away a potential touchdown pass Friday 
against Lynwood. Latario Rachal was the receiver. 
</P>
</CORRECTION>
